Red mahogany logs are used in the One Small Favour quest. They are obtained by giving a sharpened axe to the Jungle Forester near the Kharazi Jungle, south-east of Shilo Village. More logs can be obtained for 200 coins each.

The quest is completed after delivering the log to Yanni Salika in the antiques shop in the village. Warning: Yanni Salika will take all the Red mahogany logs in the player's inventory!

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
9 August 2005
(update)
  • The item was renamed from "Mahogany log" to "Red mahogany log".
  • The item's examine was changed from "Some rare mahogany logs." to "Some rare mahogany logs which have been professionally cured."
  • The item was graphically updated to distinguish it from Mahogany logs.
11 July 2005
(update)

The item was graphically updated with the release of Farming.
